@startuml
!theme plain
title Google AI Platform Training Job Notification - Data Flow

participant "AI Platform\nTraining Job" as AIJob
participant "Google Cloud\nLogging" as Logging
participant "Logging Sink" as Sink
participant "ai_platform_log\nPub/Sub Topic" as LogTopic
participant "Cloud Function\n(main.py)" as Function
participant "Notification\nPub/Sub Topic" as NotifyTopic
participant "Subscriber" as Subscriber

== Job State Change ==
AIJob -> Logging: Generate log entry\n(State: QUEUED/SUCCEEDED/FAILED/CANCELLED)
activate Logging

Logging -> Sink: Forward AI Platform logs
activate Sink

Sink -> LogTopic: Publish log message
activate LogTopic
deactivate Sink
deactivate Logging

== Log Processing ==
LogTopic -> Function: Trigger Cloud Function\n(Pub/Sub event)
activate Function

Function -> Function: Parse log message\n(Extract job state, job ID,\nproject ID, timestamp)

alt Valid Job State Detected
    Function -> NotifyTopic: Publish notification message\n{job_id, project_id,\ntimestamp, job_state}
    activate NotifyTopic

    NotifyTopic -> Subscriber: Deliver notification
    activate Subscriber
    Subscriber --> NotifyTopic: Acknowledge
    deactivate Subscriber
    deactivate NotifyTopic

    Function --> LogTopic: Processing complete
else Invalid or Unparseable Log
    Function -> Function: Handle error\n(Log error/skip)
    Function --> LogTopic: Processing complete
end

deactivate Function
deactivate LogTopic

@enduml
